  <name>AinCore Notes</name>
  <summary>AI-driven local knowledge management application</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      AinCore Notes is a local-first, AI-powered knowledge management application built on MuyaJS WYSIWYG editor. It features real-time preview editing, AI-assisted writing, BM25 full-text search with Chinese segmentation, and an MCP protocol server for external tool integration.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>WYSIWYG editing with MuyaJS (27 ContentState mixins, Snabbdom VDOM)</li>
      <li>AI-assisted writing: continuation, polishing, translation, and summarization</li>
      <li>BM25 full-text search with jieba-wasm Chinese segmentation and RRF fusion</li>
      <li>MCP stdio server: 5 tools + 1 resource for external integration</li>
      <li>Three-tier AI resilience: SDK → UDS → offline degradation</li>
      <li>Privacy interceptor with configurable PII detection</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
